summary: Multiple Australian news sources are reporting on the disappearance of two Perth brothers, Jake and Callum Robinson, who went missing while surfing in Mexico. A burnt-out ute belonging to the missing brothers was also found, and police made a grim discovery during the search for the surfers. The parents of the missing brothers have expressed gratitude for the support they have received and are traveling to Mexico to assist in the investigation. The case remains under investigation, and concerns are growing for the well-being of the missing individuals.
